{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2412b17bf5","title":"薄一波对北京地质学院问题的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b2028376ed","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"2412b17bf5"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"bc40efb1fd","name":"薄一波"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bd8a9c6e4b","type":"title","text":"薄一波对北京地质学院问题的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"},{"id":"ed2276f358","type":"authors","text":"薄一波","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"},{"id":"df460875f2","type":"appellation","text":"六月二十二日，薄一波作了一个对北京地质学院问题批示，批示全文如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"},{"id":"9e695ea598","type":"appellation","text":"人林同志并长工、光义同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"},{"id":"c4a75e797c","type":"paragraph","text":"应该明确答复学生，李主任讲的话是对的。工作组是上级党委派去的，它是代表党组织工作的，要号召左派起来跟工作队一起进行文化大革命，如果院党委有问题了，派工作队去行使党委职权，这就是等于夺回了党的领导权。如果再有人非赶走工作队不可，那势必是夺工作队之权，亦即夺党的领导权，那么谁来掌权呢？工作队有缺点、错误，可以改正，但不能给工作队随便加上什么“保皇派“之名称。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"},{"id":"34297afc33","type":"paragraph","text":" 薄一波6月22日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5"}],"page":{"id":"ccfa2c6766","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"2412b17bf5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}